data.description: Book your private showing today to see this charming home in Ogden, Utah. It offers a unique blend of historical character and modern updates. The home features a spacious living room and large windows that fill the space with natural light. The kitchen has been recently renovated with stainless steel appliances and ample storage space. There are three bedrooms, providing plenty of room for a growing family or guests. The backyard is perfect for outdoor entertaining with a patio and one car garage. To top it off, the home has a new roof and new water heater installed in 2020.  Located close to parks, schools, and shopping. Don't miss the opportunity to own this piece of Ogden's history!  Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from county records.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
